# LD feature implementation

## Module layout

- Feature modules live under `packages/model-viewer/src/features/ld-*` or `src/features/ld-*/`
- Co-locate specs in `src/test/features/` or adjacent `*-spec.ts`

## Mixin registration

Register new mixins in the `ModelViewerElementImpl` chain in [`model-viewer.ts`](../../packages/model-viewer/src/model-viewer.ts). Follow existing import style and nesting order.

## Reuse

Prefer extending existing LD utilities (`ld-debug`, `ld-utils`, transform events, selection outline) over duplicating logic.

## Docs & examples

When adding public API surface, update `docs.json`, `examples.json`, and an `ld_*` example page — see `docs-and-examples-registry.mdc`.
